wetri %VERSION%
https://github.com/fukawi2/wetri

wetri is a wrapper that will attempt to execute a task X number of times,
automatically retrying if the task fails.

===============================================================================

    INSTALLATION.

Install everything:
    make all

Install only the script:
    make bin

Install only the docs:
    make docs

Uninstallation is also catered for:
    make uninstall

===============================================================================

    USAGE.






